name: FedEx MD-10-10F [N381FE] Landing and Takeoff at San Diego ᴴᴰ
description:
WARNING! Loud engine noise after the intro!

Here we have a Federal Express McDonnell Douglas MD-10-10F landing and taking off at San Diego International Airport. Sorry for the lack of approach footage, I was packing up my tripod after British Airways landed and didn't see this guy until he was on short final. The takeoff is filmed from my hotel. Hope you enjoy, and don't forget to watch in 1080p for best quality!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
